testcase.name: usptoAllyTest

failure.message:
Found 7 accessibility violations: 1) ARIA attributes must conform to valid values: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.5/aria-valid-attr-value?application=axeAPI a) ["a[href$=\"\\#newsTab\"]"] Fix all of the following: Invalid ARIA attribute value: aria-controls="news"
b) ["a[href$=\"\\#eventsTab\"]"] Fix all of the following: Invalid ARIA attribute value: aria-controls="events"
c) ["a[href$=\"\\#remarksTab\"]"] Fix all of the following: Invalid ARIA attribute value: aria-controls="remarks"
2) id attribute value must be unique: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.5/duplicate-id?application=axeAPI a) ["script[defer=\"\"][type=\"text\\/javascript\"]:nth-child(42)"] Fix any of the following: Document has multiple static elements with the same id attribute
3) Form elements should have a visible label: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.5/label-title-only?application=axeAPI a) ["#headerSearchInput"] Fix all of the following: Only title used to generate label for form element
4) Main landmark must not be contained in another landmark: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.5/landmark-main-is-top-level?application=axeAPI a) ["#content"] Fix any of the following: The main landmark is contained in another landmark.
5) Document must not have more than one main landmark: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.5/landmark-no-duplicate-main?application=axeAPI a) ["#main"] Fix any of the following: Document has more than one main landmark
6) Ensures landmarks are unique: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.5/landmark-unique?application=axeAPI a) ["#uspto-top-nav"] Fix any of the following: The landmark must have a unique aria-label, aria-labelledby, or title to make landmarks distinguishable
b) ["#main"] Fix any of the following: The landmark must have a unique aria-label, aria-labelledby, or title to make landmarks distinguishable
7) Page must contain a level-one heading: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.5/page-has-heading-one?application=axeAPI a) ["html"] Fix all of the following: Page must have a level-one heading
expected [true] but found [false]
